Name: BIT.TRIP FATE
About the game: FATE is the penultimate chapter in the six-part BIT.TRIP series and will leave you wondering what’s next. Key Features: The arrow keys control CommanderVideo while the mouse allows you to fire anywhere on screen! Or if you prefer, plug in a controller for dual-stick shooting action! Collect power-ups to call on CommanderVideo’s friends for powerful shot upgrades! A chiptune-inspired dubstep soundtrack helps bring the action to a whole new level! Video game worlds collide with appearances from Super Meat Boy and Mr. Robotube! Chipmusic artist Minusbaby helps set the tone with a special guest appearance! Enjoy brand new Easy and Hard Difficulty Modes! Ride the vibe in BIT.TRIP FATE to discover where CommanderVideo’s true mission will take him.
